container_info.post_install_tip: To begin work with add-on, you need to click on the "OpenCalls.me" button in the top menu. After that press the "Start" button to start working with add-on. If you need more information about add-on or help just click "FAQ" button in "OpenCalls.me" tab.

name: OpenCalls.me
description: OpenCalls.me saves detailed call history from your Android phone to Google Drive, lets you analyze customer calls and send emails.
